Raxttrogit dexobhkticher adaril'lem ani maibhuyevixincho ador, obhiman vyokt korpi ek raxttri-i git. Raxttrant ekcharachi bhauna vaddik lagchi ani raxttravixincho obhiman sondach zagrit urcho hea ud'dexan dor ek raxttr aplo bautto (dhvoz), aplem raxttri-i protik va rajyomudra, raxttri-i suknnem, raxttri-i zonaur ani raxttrogit heo gozali tharoita. Him raxttri-i protikam tea tea raxttracho mamdondd asun dor ek nagrik tanchevixim ador ani obhiman ballgita. Raxttr – rajeachi kolpona thir zatkoch raxttrogitachi kolpona ostitvant aili.

I. So. 1825 to grett brittnan suru kel'lem raxttrogit hem ady somzotat. Otthravea xotmanachea modegakosaun brittnan rajdorobarant dor eka somarombhache survek raxttrogit mhonnpachi chal suru keli ani uprant ekonnisavea xotmanache survek zaitea yuropi-i raxttramni hi protha apnnaili. Raxttrogitant raxttrobhkti, raxttrabhiman ani raxttrachi vijeagatha gunthil'li asa. ‘zongonnomon’ ani ‘vonde matrom'’ him bhartachim don raxttrogitam asat. Hatuntolem zongonnomon hem raxttrogit ek vhodd bongali sahityik rovindronath ttagor hannem rochlam. 27 ddisembor 1911 hea disa inddiyon nexnol kangresoche raxttri-i sobheche machyer tem poile khep gayil'lem. 24 zanevari 1950 hea disa bharti-i ghottna porixoden ‘zongonnomon’ hea gitantlean fokot poilea koddveak raxttrogitachi manyotai dili. Vonde matrom'‘ hem somskritoprochur oxem bongali bhaxentolem git bongali sahityik bonkimochondr chottrji hannem boroil'lem (sumar 1870).

1882 to tem anond motth he kadomborit ujvaddak ailem. Inddiyon nexnol kangreschea i. So. 1895 che sobhevellar tem poile khep gayil'lem. Bongaloche fallnnik virodh kelo. Zongonnomon ani vonde matrom' hea gitakhatir vad chalu astonach ponddit nehruche sangnnen akaxovanni kendrar zongonnomon hem git sador korunk lailem. Nehruche sangnnen akaxovanni kendran hea gitachi chal bosoun tem 1 mintta bhitor mhonnun bi.Bi.Si kodden dilem. Fuddem horbott myurril hannem taka sodeachi chal dili. Him raxttrogitam oxim asat – vonde matrom' sujlam suflam moloizoxitolam sosyoxamolam matrom' xubhrojeotsom' pulkitoyaminim' ful'lokusumitdrumodoloxobhinim' suhasini sumdhurobhaxinnim sukhdam vordam matrom' ।। kotti kotti bhuzoi dhritoi – khor – korvale ke bole ma lumi obol bohubol – dharinnim nomami tarinnim ripudolovarinnim matrom' ।। tumi videa tumi dhorm' tumi hrdi tumi morm' tvom hi pranna : xorire bahu te tumi ma xokti hdoye tumi ma bhokti to marodd protima goddi mondire mondire । tvom hi durga doxprohoronnodharinni komla komlodoloviharinni vanni videadayini nomami tvam nomami komlam omlam otulam sujlam suflam, matrom' । vond -bonkimochondr chottrji

